first version of background image and sound notification. If you want to hear ringthones, click any button. Add handler_mouse and first 
version button(CLICKBAIT(LOL))
click on personal settings or Sign for any Size Window, code can follow it.
RUN:
_______________________________
g++ -c paint.cpp
g++ paint.o -o paint -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-system -lsfml-audio -lssh -lstdc++fs
./paint
